Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: django-admin-locking
Version: 0.7.1
Summary: A reusable app for locking objects within the admin while another editoris editing the page.
Home-page: https://dev.jonasundderwolf.de/opensource/django-admin-locking/
Author: jonasvp
Author-email: jvp@jonasundderwolf.de
License: UNKNOWN
Description: ====================
        django-admin-locking
        ====================
        
        Never lose work to another editor again!
        
        
        Add ``admin_locking`` to ``INSTALLED_APPS`` and inherit from
        ``admin_locking.AdminLockingMixin``.
        
        
        *How to add to all ModelAdmins?*
        
        Use a common parent: instead of inheriting from ``admin.ModelAdmin``,
        create a base object to inherit from.
        
